lead_paragraph: Australia captain Steve Smith shook off a sickening blow to the back of his head and notched up his 14th test century, earning the praise of his team mates and New Zealand opponents at the end of the second day of the second test on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Smith Earns Praise After Sickening Head Knock
